=== Example 018: Basic paste command ===
Using backticks to call paste (two files):
Alice	25
Bob	30
Charlie	35

paste with custom delimiter (-d ','):
Alice,25
Bob,30
Charlie,35

paste with multiple files:
Alice	25	Engineer
Bob	30	Manager
Charlie	35	Developer

paste with serial (-s):
Alice	Bob	Charlie

paste with newline delimiter (-d '\n'):
Alice
25
Bob
30
Charlie
35

paste with tab delimiter (-d '\t'):
Alice	25
Bob	30
Charlie	35

paste with zero delimiter (-d '\0'):
Alice25
Bob30
Charlie35

paste with space delimiter (-d ' '):
Alice 25
Bob 30
Charlie 35

paste with pipe delimiter (-d '|'):
Alice|25
Bob|30
Charlie|35

paste from stdin (echo | paste):
Alice	25
Bob	30
	35

paste with multiple delimiters:
Alice|25,Engineer
Bob|30,Manager
Charlie|35,Developer

paste with serial and delimiter (-s -d ','):
Alice,Bob,Charlie
